				"A hope for humanity, to find another suitable place to live in the vast universe after &aEarth&r."
				""
				"For some could be kind of harsh, but it’s the only one so far… &9Glacio&r is all &nfrozen&r. Yet has &dOxygen&r all around. When crafting the last tier of &6Rockets&r, your &bSpace Exploring&r map will yet again have a new option."
				""
				"The new &eSolar System&r to explore has only a planet, which is &9Glacio&r. And it’s called &5Proxima Century&r."
				""
				"Doesn’t have a star like we do, is purple… and bigger. Doesn’t have a hostile creature. But only a single passive. The &dGlacian Ram&r."
				""
				"These are the ores found on the planet &9Glacio&r. Moreover, this planet's height/layers are similar to &aEarth&r/&aOverworld&r. Meaning there’s a &0Deepslate&r layer, although in this layer only rare minerals of the shown above would be generated."
