				""
				"Inserting a &bSpace Suit&r (Chestsplate), the set will be given &dOxygen&r, depending on how badly it’s the planet that you're on. &dOxygen&r will be consumed rapidly or simply none. If on &aEarth&r, or in a place where &dOxygen&r it’s given constantly, the &dOxygen&r from the Suit &nwon’t be consumed&r!"
